- Sort: `lastModified desc`
- Capture: `modelId`, `createdAt`, `lastModified`, tags, `library_name`, file list, license

### 2) CPU-optimized variants
For each candidate, check for:
- `onnx`, `gguf`, `int8`, `q8`, `coreml`, `safetensors`
- Quantized/pruned variants **post-2025-10-31** (variant date qualifies)
- File size + required runtime (onnxruntime, ggml, etc.)

### 3) Vendor docs / announcements
- Verify release/update date with an authoritative source
